\section{四次多项式的Galois群}

设$f(x)=x^{4}+bx^{3}+cx^{2}+dx+e$是$K$上的不可约多项式，$f(x)$没有重根，$E$为$f(x)$的分裂域，在$E$上有$f(x)=(x-\alpha_{1})(x-\alpha_{2})(x-\alpha_{3})(x-\alpha_{4})$，我们先假定$G_{f}=S_{4}$。\par

对于

\centerline{
\xymatrix@C=2ex{
    K\ar[d] & \subseteq & K(\Delta(f))\ar[d] & \subseteq & M\ar[d] & \subseteq & E\ar[d]  \\
    S_{4} & \rhd & A_{4} & \rhd & K_{4} & \rhd & \{id\}
    }
}\par
\vspace{2em}
我们想求出$K_{4}$对应的Galois群$M$，$M$中元素是在$K_{4}$作用下不动的。

令
\begin{equation}
\left\{
\begin{aligned}
\beta_{1}=\alpha_{1}\alpha_{2}+\alpha_{3}\alpha_{4}\nonumber\\
\beta_{2}=\alpha_{1}\alpha_{3}+\alpha_{2}\alpha_{4}\nonumber\\
\beta_{3}=\alpha_{1}\alpha_{4}+\alpha_{2}\alpha_{3}\nonumber\\
\end{aligned}
\right.
\end{equation}\par
我们发现$\{\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3}\}$在$K_{4}$作用下还是
$\{\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3}\}$。$K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3})$ 对应的中间群为$Gal(E/K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3}))$，而$Gal(E/K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3}))=\{\tau\in S_{4}\mid \tau(\beta_{i})=\beta_{i},i=1,2,3\}$，经过计算得到，$Gal(E/K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3}))=K_{4}=\{(1),(12)(34),(13)(24),(14)(23)\}$，也就是说$M=K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3})$。\par

容易验证，$\{\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3})\}$在$S_{4}$的作用下是一条轨道。设$g(x)=(x-\beta_{1})(x-\beta_{2})(x-\beta_{3})$，则$g(x)$在$G_{f}$的作用下是不变的。$G_{f}$中元素为$K-\text{同构}$，所以$g(x)\in K[x]$，且$K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3})$为$g(x)$的分裂域。\par

$g(x)=x^{3}-(\beta_{1}+\beta_{2}+\beta_{3})x^{2}+(\beta_{1}\beta_{2}+\beta_{1}\beta_{3}+\beta_{2}\beta_{3})x+
\beta_{1}\beta_{2}\beta_{3}$\\
其中$\beta_{1}+\beta_{2}+\beta_{3}=\alpha_{1}\alpha_{2}+\alpha_{1}\alpha_{3}+\alpha_{1}\alpha_{4}+\alpha_{2}\alpha_{3}+
\alpha_{2}\alpha_{4}+\alpha_{3}\alpha_{4}=\sigma_{2}=c$，$\beta_{1}\beta_{2}+\beta_{1}\beta_{3}+\beta_{2}\beta_{3}$是对称的，将$\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3}$代入后展开，按次数排列有两项$(2,1,1,0)$和$(1,1,1,1)$，则$\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3}$ 可化为$A\sigma_{1}\sigma_{3}+B\sigma_{4}$，用待定系数法可确定$A=1$，$B=-4$。同样，$\beta_{1}\beta_{2}\beta_{3}$展开后有$(3,1,1,1)$，$(2,2,2,0)$，$(2,2,1,1)$，可表示成$A\sigma_{1}^{2}\sigma_{4}+B\sigma_{3}^{2}+C\sigma_{2}\sigma_{4}$，用待定系数法求得$A=-1$，$B=-1$，$C=4$，则有
\begin{equation}
\left.
\begin{aligned}
g(x)=&x^{3}-\sigma_{2}x^{2}+(\sigma_{1}\sigma_{3}-4\sigma_{4})x-\sigma_{1}^{2}\sigma_{4}-\sigma_{3}^{2}+4\sigma_{2}\sigma_{4}\nonumber\\
=&x^{3}-cx^{2}+(bd-4e)x-b^{2}e-d^{2}+4ce\nonumber\\
\end{aligned}
\right.
\end{equation}\par

由于$\beta_{1}-\beta_{2}=\alpha_{1}\alpha_{2}+\alpha_{3}\alpha_{4}-\alpha_{1}\alpha_{3}-\alpha_{2}\alpha_{4}=(\alpha_{1}-
\alpha_{4})(\alpha_{2}-\alpha_{3})$，$\beta_{1}-\beta_{3}=(\alpha_{1}-\alpha_{3})(\alpha_{2}-\alpha_{4})$，
$\beta_{2}-\beta_{3}=(\alpha_{1}-\alpha_{2})(\alpha_{3}-\alpha_{4})$
\begin{equation}
\left.
\begin{aligned}
\Delta(g)=&(\beta_{1}-\beta_{2})(\beta_{1}-\beta_{3})(\beta_{2}-\beta_{3})\nonumber\\
=&(\alpha_{1}-\alpha_{4})(\alpha_{2}-\alpha_{3})(\alpha_{1}-\alpha_{3})(\alpha_{2}-\alpha_{4})(\alpha_{1}-\alpha_{2})(\alpha_{3}-\alpha_{4})\nonumber\\
=&\Delta(f)\nonumber\\
\end{aligned}
\right.
\end{equation}\par

因此计算四次多项式的$\Delta(f)$可转化为计算三次多项式的$\Delta(g)$。\par
\vspace{2em}
前面的过程都在假定$f(x)$的Galois群是$S_{4}$的前提下，那么给了一个$K$上的四次不可约多项式$f(x)$ （$K$的特征为$0$）。我们来确定它的Galois群。\par

首先计算$g(x)$。$K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3})$是$g(x)$的分裂域。$G_{g}$为$g(x)$的Galois群。然后判断$g(x)$在$K$上是否可约。若$g(x)$不可约，可通过前面计算三次多项式Galois群的方法来计算$G_{g}$。若$g(x)$可约，则$g(x)$可写成三个一次因式或一个一次因式和一个二次因式的乘积，$G_{g}$的计算就更容易了。\par

$Gal(E/K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3}))=K_{4}\cap G_{f}$，由于$K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3})$为$g(x)$的分裂域，$K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3})/K$是Galois扩张，由Galois 基本定理，$G_{g}\cong G_{f}/K_{4}\cap G_{f}$。\par

\centerline{
\xymatrix@C=2ex{
    K\ar[d] & \subseteq & K(\Delta(f))\ar[d] & \subseteq & K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3})\ar[d] & \subseteq & E\ar[d]  \\
    S_{4}\ar[d] & \rhd & A_{4}\ar[d] & \rhd & K_{4}\ar[d] & \rhd & \{id\}\ar[d] \\
    G_{f} & \rhd & A_{4}\cap G_{f} & \rhd & K_{4}\cap G_{f} & \rhd & \{id\}
    }
}\par
\vspace{2em}
又因为$4\mid |G_{f}|$，所以$G_{f}$有以下几种情况\par
\centerline{
\begin{tabular}{|c|c|c|}
  \hline
  % after \\: \hline or \cline{col1-col2} \cline{col3-col4} ...
  $|G_{g}|$ & $|G_{f}|$ & $G_{f}$ \\ \hline
  6 & 24 & $S_{4}$ \\ \hline
  3 & 12 & $A_{4}$ \\ \hline
  2 & 8 & $D_{4}\cong K_{4}\{(1),(12)\}$ \\ \hline
  2 & 4 & $C_{4}\cong <(1234)>$ \\ \hline
  1 & 4 & $K_{4}$ \\
  \hline
\end{tabular}
}\par
\vspace{2em}
因此，我们可以通过$g(x)$来计算$G_{g}$，然后根据表格来推断出$G_{f}$，当$|G_{g}|=2$时，$G_{f}=D_{4}\text{或}C_{4}$。下面看$f(x)$在$K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3})$上是否可约，当$f(x)$在$K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3})$上不可约时，$K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3})$对应的Galois群在$f(x)$的根的集合$\{\alpha_{1},\alpha_{2},\alpha_{3},\alpha_{4}\}$ 上是传递的，$G_{f}$只能是$D_{4}$，若是$C_{4}$的话，$K_{4}\cap C_{4}$中有两个元素，在$\{\alpha_{1},\alpha_{2},\alpha_{3},\alpha_{4}\}$ 上是不传递的。当$f(x)$在$K(\beta_{1},\beta_{2},\beta_{3})$上可约时，$G_{f}=C_{4}$。
\vspace{2em}

例：$f(x)=x^{4}-4x+2\in Q[x]$，由Eisenstein判别法可知，$f(x)$在$Q$上不可约。$g(x)=x^{3}-8x+16$ 在$Q$上不可约，$(\Delta(f))^{2}=(\Delta(g))^{2}=-4864$，所以$\Delta(g)\notin Q$，则$G_{g}=S_{3}$。查表可得，$G_{f}=S_{4}$。\par

例：$f(x)=x^{4}+4x^{2}+2\in Q[x]$，由Eisenstein 判别法可知，$f(x)$在$Q$上不可约。$g(x)=(x-4)(x^{2}-8)$，分裂域为$M=Q(\sqrt{2})$，$|G_{g}|=2$，而$f(x)$在$Q(\sqrt{2})$上可约，所以$G_{f}=C_{4}$。\par

例：$f(x)=x^{4}-10x^{2}+4\in Q[x]$，因为在$Q$上没有根，$f(x)$在$Q$上不可约。$g(x)=(x+10)(x+4)(x-4)$，$|G_{g}|=1$。查表可得，$G_{f}=K_{4}$。\par


